## 18. Summary

This design provides:
- Secure SPA auth for web (cookies + CSRF)
- Device-based token auth for mobile/integrations
- Tenant-scoped RBAC with presets + custom roles
- CA↔Business relationship with mandatory approval + controlled staff access
- Strong audit logging and safe impersonation

**Next step (when ready):** turn this into implementation tasks:
- migrations
- middleware (tenant resolver)
- auth controllers for web/mobile
- membership services
- CA relationship services
- audit event pipeline
- role/permission seeding per tenant type
